### CurrencyAPI.com Tests (Requires API key)
# API key is loaded from .env file
@apiKey = {{$dotenv CURRENCYAPI_KEY}}

### Get latest rates
GET https://api.currencyapi.com/v3/latest?apikey={{apiKey}}&base_currency=USD&currencies=GBP,EUR,JPY

###

### Get historical rates for specific date
GET https://api.currencyapi.com/v3/historical?apikey={{apiKey}}&base_currency=USD&currencies=GBP,EUR&date=2024-01-31

###

### Convert currency (if supported)
GET https://api.currencyapi.com/v3/convert?apikey={{apiKey}}&from=USD&to=GBP&value=100

###

### Get list of available currencies
GET https://api.currencyapi.com/v3/currencies?apikey={{apiKey}}

###

### Get rates for multiple base currencies
GET https://api.currencyapi.com/v3/latest?apikey={{apiKey}}&base_currency=USD

